{"text_id":28915,"tokens":["The"," use"," of"," mobile"," phones"," while"," driving"," has"," become"," a"," significant"," issue"," of"," concern"," in"," recent"," times","."," With"," the"," rapid"," advancement"," of"," technology"," and"," the"," ubi","quity"," of"," smartphones",","," it"," has"," become"," increasingly"," challenging"," for"," drivers"," to"," resist"," the"," temptation"," of"," using"," their"," phones"," while"," behind"," the"," wheel","."," However",","," the"," dangers"," of"," using"," a"," phone"," while"," driving"," cannot"," be"," over","stated","."," This"," behavior"," can"," result"," in"," severe"," consequences",","," including"," traffic"," accidents",","," injuries",","," and"," fatalities","."," In"," this"," essay",","," I"," will"," argue"," that"," using"," a"," phone"," while"," driving"," is"," a"," hazardous"," behavior"," that"," should"," not"," be"," normalized",","," supported"," by"," statistics"," and"," examples",".","\n\n","Firstly",","," it"," is"," important"," to"," highlight"," that"," using"," a"," phone"," while"," driving"," significantly"," increases"," the"," risk"," of"," traffic"," accidents","."," According"," to"," the"," National"," Highway"," Traffic"," Safety"," Administration"," (","NH","TSA","),"," driving"," while"," distracted"," caused"," ","3",",","1","4","2"," deaths"," in"," ","2","0","1","9",","," accounting"," for"," ","9","%"," of"," all"," traffic"," fatalities"," (","NH","TSA",","," ","2","0","2","1",")."," Additionally",","," research"," has"," shown"," that"," texting"," while"," driving"," can"," make"," a"," driver"," ","2","3"," times"," more"," likely"," to"," be"," involved"," in"," a"," crash"," (","Virginia"," Tech"," Transportation"," Institute",","," ","2","0","1","3",")."," These"," statistics"," demonstrate"," the"," significant"," danger"," associated"," with"," using"," a"," phone"," while"," driving"," and"," the"," need"," to"," address"," this"," issue",".","\n\n